{"tid":1981370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民調: 超過80%英國人 要求英國政府撤查「中共」","createTime":"2020-04-20T15:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T20:37:05.000Z","uid":134071,"like":552,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"eda3ca758cd33b1e6005824392e0c13f25603dc3","tid":1981370,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"Henry Jackson Society民調: <br />\n<br />\n- 超過80%英國人 要求英國政府撤查「中共」抗疫手法<br />\n- 71%英國人 認為英國需要控告「中共」 (如果調查證實「中共」抗疫手法違反國際法)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/britons-want-china-to-face-inquiry-over-coronavirus-outbreak-cbm82lpvk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fbritons-want-china-to-face-inquiry-over-coronavirus-outbreak-cbm82lpvk&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=e9f0f904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/britons-want-china-to-face-inquiry-over-coronavirus-outbreak-cbm82lpvk</a><br />\n<br />\nBritons want China to face inquiry over coronavirus outbreak<br />\nLucy Fisher, Defence Editor<br />\nMonday April 20 2020, 12.01am BST, The Times<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMore than 80 per cent of Britons want Boris Johnson to push for an international inquiry into China&rsquo;s handling of the initial coronavirus outbreak, according to a poll.<br />\n<br />\nThe survey also revealed that 71 per cent of the public wanted ministers to sue the Chinese government for damages if it became evident that President Xi&rsquo;s administration had breached international law in its response to the coronavirus.<br />\n<br />\nThe poll, commissioned last week by the Henry Jackson Society, a British neoconservative foreign affairs think tank, showed that 74 per cent of the UK public thought that China was to blame for allowing Covid-19 to spread."},{"pid":"ea54b955ea167cef69006930b7456d0eae0365cc","tid":1981370,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020