03e","tid":1981370,"uid":148315,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:42:04.000Z","msg":"唔係「中國」咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫住China<br />\n中國共產黨同中國根本分唔開<br />\n支那人沒有一個是無辜的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:42:48.000Z","msg":"<em>The survey also revealed that 71 per cent of the public wanted ministers to sue the <strong>Chinese government</strong> for damages if it became evident that President Xi&rsquo;s administration had breached international law in its response to the coronavirus.</em>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"Chinese government 咪中國囉"},{"pid":"c137aba7e08a92b728270c63556d816da8fa5d65","tid":1981370,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37ded6f4a54945c31f0bbbf0f014943721bad023","tid":1981370,"uid":283912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f19e04675d58ed2bcda4fb1b61eabc8592737ea","tid":1981370,"uid":304769,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"大家要今次好好engage英國啊，係好機會啊<br />\n<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，英國點日落都好，都係重要持分者，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要拉攏英國民意啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:27:28.000Z","msg":"Agger,唔好lable咗人日落就放棄呢條線<br />\n英國就算唔幫香港出手但跟美帝隊幫手隊死支那都夠"},{"pid":"1ed26d1de6d91bec84158aa17e5428a8f5ccd039","tid":1981370,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:31:50.000Z","msg":"up，殺死中共"},{"pid":"6292824ce453633f68d99522b01045d2f172c902","tid":1981370,"uid":56819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實而家係點架，政府奶共國民反共？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本上全世界大部份國家都係奶共,但人民就普遍反共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461b8e9c975b10c666a60a72f096e9d2845ceaf8","tid":1981370,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0f3efdc49b3bbb46d65e05adb8ad6c230b599b","tid":1981370,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借個位先 召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=1d7cb989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"537a5988718a1467f8680886fef7686b3cc935e3","tid":19813