on Society, a British neoconservative foreign affairs think tank, showed that 74 per cent of the UK public thought that China was to blame for allowing Covid-19 to spread."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"撤查係唔查,徹查係徹底查"},{"pid":"1280d8f8e1376c064520478b87d8c077411f1248","tid":1981370,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"Tweet 在此 上去Twitter 推下啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/thetimes/status/1252168795847868417?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthetimes%2Fstatus%2F1252168795847868417%3Fs%3D20&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=14cde3f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthetimes%2Fstatus%2F1252168795847868417%3Fs%3D20&h=e2425bd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/thetimes/status/1252168795847868417?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"84cfb4244c8466e980fe1e0f85bb0b2baa325119","tid":1981370,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:00:17.000Z","msg":"#MakeChinaPay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b260bdb1d6d0a54889564cbdd816dad08dade7aa","tid":1981370,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"你今日tweet左未？"},{"pid":"475386fb404c4699780a273db578ed49b543bfe1","tid":1981370,"uid":287461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f19e04675d58ed2bcda4fb1b61eabc8592737ea","tid":1981370,"uid":304769,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"大家要今次好好engage英國啊，係好機會啊<br />\n<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，英國點日落都好，都係重要持分者，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要拉攏英國民意啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17